sentence-with-vars: Does instructor0 always set exams for their classes ?
sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.HAS_EXAMS FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 INNER JOIN COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 ON COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID INNER JOIN OFFERING_INSTRUCTOR AS OFFERING_INSTRUCTORalias0 ON OFFERING_INSTRUCTORalias0.OFFERING_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.OFFERING_ID INNER JOIN INSTRUCTOR AS INSTRUCTORalias0 ON OFFERING_INSTRUCTORalias0.INSTRUCTOR_ID = INSTRUCTORalias0.INSTRUCTOR_ID WHERE INSTRUCTORalias0.NAME LIKE "%smith%" ;
